<section>
    <article>
        <details {% if not subservice %}class="persistent" open{% endif %}>
            <summary class="rightSummary aboutSection">About</summary>
            <p>This is BIC Tracker, meant for tracking changes in Bank Identification Codes issued by <a href="https://cbr.ru/" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" class="linkIcon" src="/img/tech/CBR.svg" alt="Central Bank of Russia">Центральный Банк Российской Федерации</a> (Central Bank of Russia or CBR).</p>
            <p>The library contains different information used by banks and other parties to identify both the banks themselves and services provided by them. The tracker is meant to provide a visual representation of that information and also track some of the changes to it.</p>
            <p>There is also an "official" forum thread on <a href="https://www.banki.ru/forum/?PAGE_NAME=read&FID=29&TID=324456" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" class="linkIcon" src="/img/icons/banki.ru.svg" alt="Central Bank of Russia">banki.ru</a></p>
            {% if not subservice %}
                <p>You are on the main page of the service. To search for bank details, please, use <a href="/bictracker/search/" target="_self" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">Search</span></a>. If you are looking for account control number checker use <a href="/bictracker/keying/" target="_self" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">keying</span></a> page.</p>
            {% endif %}
        </details>
    </article>
    {% if subservice %}
        <article lang="ru-RU">
            {% if subservice == 'keying' %}
                {{ include('bictracker/keying.twig')}}
            {% elseif subservice == 'search' %}
                {{ include('bictracker/search.twig')}}
            {% elseif subservice == 'bic' %}
                {{ include('bictracker/bic.twig')}}
            {% endif %}
        </article>
    {% endif %}
</section>
